fix(extension): add metadata extraction fallbacks and fix URL matching

Implement regex-based text extraction as a fallback when primary DOM selectors fail for fields like DOI, journal, volume, issue, pages, and ISSNs. This ensures data is captured even if the page structure differs from expected selectors.

Update diagnostic article lookup in background.js to normalize URLs by stripping fragments and checking prefixes, resolving issues where status tracking failed due to URL variations.
